    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skills",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/35428890/ad8a357fa8480f61f3fe665b69d9c263_4695189778021278055.png",
                "id": "talent35407",
                "key": "Cutting Torrent",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Cutting Torrent"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Switches to <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melee Stance</span> and deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>, and attach Riptide to the target character.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Melee Stance</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span> dealt by character is converted to <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After the character uses Charged Attack:</span> Apply <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Riptide </span>to target character.</p><p>Character deals +1 DMG to target characters with <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Riptide </span>attached.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After Skills are used against characters affected by Riptide</span>: Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Piercing DMG</span> to the next opposing off-field character. (Twice per Round)</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds): 2</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Riptide</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When the character to which this is attached is defeated</span>: Apply Riptide to active character.</p><p>(When <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Tartaglia </span>is in <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melee Stance</span>, he will deal additional DMG when attacking the character to which this is attached.)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/35428890/dbae3420341a6acd9d59fdbb7fbc1a95_1914777810032723966.png",
                "id": "talent74044",
                "key": "Foul Legacy: Raging Tide",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Foul Legacy: Raging Tide"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Performs different attacks based on the current stance that <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Tartaglia </span>is in.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Ranged Stance - Flash of Havoc:</span> Deal 5 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>, reclaim 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Energy</span>, and apply <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Riptide </span>to the target character.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melee Stance - Light of Obliteration:</span> Deal 7 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Riptide</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When the character to which this is attached is defeated</span>: Apply Riptide to active character.</p><p>(When <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Tartaglia </span>is in <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melee Stance</span>, he will deal additional DMG when attacking the character to which this is attached.)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/35428890/7cb5ba8ac0510bfb42e1bde894444ec4_3009872402527687558.png",
                "id": "talent27293",
                "key": "Havoc: Obliteration",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Havoc: Obliteration"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Passive Skill</span></p><p>(Passive) When the battle begins, this character gains <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Ranged Stance</span>. Once the <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melee Stance</span> attached to the character ends, reapplies <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Ranged Stance</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Ranged Stance</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After the character to which this is attached uses Charged Attack</span>: Apply <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Riptide </span>to target character.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Riptide</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When the character to which this is attached is defeated</span>: Apply Riptide to active character.</p><p>(When <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Tartaglia </span>is in <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melee Stance</span>, he will deal additional DMG when attacking the character to which this is attached.)</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds): 2</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Melee Stance</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span> dealt by character is converted to <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After the character uses Charged Attack:</span> Apply <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Riptide </span>to target character.</p><p>Character deals +1 DMG to target characters with <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Riptide </span>attached.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After Skills are used against characters affected by Riptide</span>: Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Piercing DMG</span> to the next opposing off-field character. (Twice per Round)</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds): 2</span></p><p></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/35428890/3e90a55bd72193eae8ddd2475b84577d_9009068752035438776.png",
                "id": "talent47981",
                "key": "Tide Withholder",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Tide Withholder"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Hydro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Vaporize</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Frozen</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, the target is unable to perform any Actions this Round (Can be removed in advance after the target receives +2 Physical or Pyro DMG)</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Bloom</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] that grants +2 DMG to the next instance of Pyro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/35428890/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_2095985709173488756.png",
                "id": "talent46949",
                "key": "Hydro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Hydro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Charged Attack</span></strong></p><p>Before your Action Phase, should the total number of your Elemental Dice be even, your Normal Attack will be considered a Charged Attack.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Piercing DMG</span></strong></p><p>Piercing DMG cannot be increased by any bonuses, but cannot be defended against using Shields or DMG Immunity either.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Duration (Rounds)</span></strong></p><p>Each time you reach the end of a Round, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Duration (Rounds)</span> -1.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds)</span> runs out.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Energy</span></strong></p><p>Characters must consume Energy to use their Elemental Bursts.</p><p>When characters use an Elemental Skill or a Normal Attack, they will gain 1 Energy.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_6318218308652672984.png",
                "id": "talent54635",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detailed Rules"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
